### TrinityCore Companion App - API Tests
### Use this in VSCode with REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@wowheadUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/wowhead
@itemsUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/items
@playersUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/players
@serverUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/server

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###
### ===== WoWHead Integration Tests =====
###

### Get Thunderfury (Legendary Sword)
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/items/19019

### Get Sulfuras (Epic Weapon)
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/items/17182

### Search for Swords
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/items/search/sword

### Search for Dragonflight Items
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/items/search/dragonflight

### Get Lich King NPC
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/npcs/36597

### Get Ragnaros NPC
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/npcs/11502

### Get Pyroblast Spell
GET {{wowheadUrl}}/spells/11366

###
### ===== TrinityCore Database Tests =====
###

### Get First 10 Items
GET {{itemsUrl}}?page=1&limit=10

### Get Specific Item (Entry 25)
GET {{itemsUrl}}/25

### Get All Players (First Page)
GET {{playersUrl}}?page=1&limit=20

### Get Online Players
GET {{playersUrl}}/online

### Get Server Status
GET {{serverUrl}}/status

### Get Server Metrics
GET {{serverUrl}}/metrics

